33:26 - Day 2: 



"I've finally made it to the front line. Horrors no man should have to witness have been my diet..: 



Skinny white dudes in shades grinding up on clearly uninterested women 29:07 - or maybe they're good friends?  Women mimicking hitting skinny white dudes 29:27, and skinny white dudes not taking the hint. Then after 10 minutes of rejection they finally take the hint and move on to other scavenging-grounds; maybe the women's port-a-potties...Dear God.


An angry bald man treating this whole ordeal like he's an usher, except no one has hired him, and so he just proceeded to... talk angrily at people and assert himself aggressively towards anyone who came too near or were having too much fun... like that tall hand-moves guy. He only had 30 seconds in the spotlight before baldman took it all away and sent him to the back, only to stand there dissatisfied and impotent - waiting for life to serve him, when in reality he's got everything he could wish for, but fails to see the wealth of his own life. I hope baldman finds the strength he needs to overcome the darkness within himself."
